{"type":null,"faqId":49889,"title":"华为智能手表_什么是影院模式？","answer":"<body style=\"clear:both; padding-left:10px; padding-top:5px; padding-right:5px; padding-bottom:5px\"><div id=\"body61783529\"><p id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022329189__p27789888\">在剧场、电影院等环境中，影院模式会使手表保持在黑屏状态，通过手势（抬腕、翻腕），点击屏幕等动作均无法唤醒屏幕，当有通知、来电时也不会唤醒。开启影院模式不会干扰他人，是既礼貌又合理的做法。</p><div class=\"note\" id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022329189__note48782404\"><img src=\"http://app.huawei.com/tkb/ha-i/7c513_bgunj.gif\"><span class=\"notetitle\"> 说明： </span><div class=\"notebody\"><p class=\"text\" id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022329189__p19180855\">影院模式并不简单等同于低功耗模式。如果开启影院模式，则无法看时间、通知及来电也无法及时看到，就失去了手表的意义，所以并不推荐在日常使用中开启。</p></div></div></div><div><div class=\"familylinks\"></div></div></body>","faqTypeId":636,"faqType":"屏幕显示类","useful":3,"unUseful":3,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"zh-cn_topic_0022329189","faqTypeCode":"Wearable_Device-Screen-Display","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1448616654000,"seriesProductName":"Mercury-G00,Mercury-G01,Mercury-G10","visitedTimes":69,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"影院模式","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}